{"type":"message","id":"1bf5bba2","parentId":"87379945","timestamp":"2026-04-08T14:05:31.899Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Port 9335 is responding with `{\"status\":\"ok\"}`. The user restarted VibeSurf on port 9335. Now I should proceed to open Google in the browser. Let me first get the browser state, then navigate to google.com."},{"type":"text","text":"服务已在 `localhost:9335` 就绪。执行浏览器测试，打开 Google：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ntc8ogbsv04g_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -X POST http://localhost:9335/api/tool/execute -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"action_name\":\"browser.navigate\",\"parameters\":{\"url\":\"https://www.google.com\"}}'"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775657127058,"responseId":"062593a745524bd111008a257cabf512"}}
{"type":"message","id":"9e459788","parentId":"1bf5bba2","timestamp":"2026-04-08T14:05:32.236Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ntc8ogbsv04g_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"success\":false,\"action_name\":\"browser.navigate\",\"result\":{\"message\":\"No LLM profile available. Please create an LLM profile first.\"},\"error\":\"llm_not_initialized\"}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":240,"aggregated":"{\"success\":false,\"action_name\":\"browser.navigate\",\"result\":{\"message\":\"No LLM profile available. Please create an LLM profile first.\"},\"error\":\"llm_not_initialized\"}","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775657132206}}
{"type":"message","id":"4f510e05","parentId":"9e459788","timestamp":"2026-04-08T14:05:37.536Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Still need LLM profile. User previously asked about this. Need to create an LLM profile. We need to know what parameters to pass. Let's check the llm-profiles endpoint to see the schema. The earlier attempt returned HTML from a Langflow UI, so maybe need to POST to a different endpoint. Let me check the docs.\n\nActually looking back at the vibesurf SKILL.md, there's a reference: `references/config-llm.md`. Let me read it to understand how to create an LLM profile."},{"type":"text","text":"仍然提示没有 LLM profile。需要先配置一个。让我查看配置方式。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_58eq7upsmjkz_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/skills/vibesurf/references/config-llm.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775657132238,"responseId":"062593ace72f5a29de3b92c69ba49b35"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f603ccd7","parentId":"4f510e05","timestamp":"2026-04-08T14:05:37.861Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_58eq7upsmjkz_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: config-llm\ndescription: Use when user asks to configure LLM profiles, manage AI model settings, add/update/remove LLM configurations, or switch between different LLM providers like OpenAI, Anthropic, Google, etc.\n---\n\n# Config LLM - LLM Profile Management\n\n## Overview\n\nManage LLM (Large Language Model) profiles for VibeSurf. Configure different AI providers, models, and their parameters.\n\n## When to Use\n\n- User wants to add a new LLM profile\n- User needs to switch default LLM\n- User wants to update LLM settings (temperature, max_tokens, etc.)\n- User needs to see available LLM providers and models\n- User wants to list or manage existing LLM profiles\n\n## API Endpoints\n\nBase path: `$VIBESURF_ENDPOINT/api/config`\n\n### Profile Management\n\n| Action | Method | Endpoint | Description |\n|--------|--------|----------|-------------|\n| List Profiles | GET | `/api/config/llm-profiles?active_only=true` | List all LLM profiles |\n| Get Profile | GET | `/api/config/llm-profiles/{profile_name}` | Get specific profile details |\n| Create Profile | POST | `/api/config/llm-profiles` | Create new LLM profile |\n| Update Profile | PUT | `/api/config/llm-profiles/{profile_name}` | Update existing profile |\n| Set Default | POST | `/api/config/llm-profiles/{profile_name}/set-default` | Set profile as default |\n| Get Default | GET | `/api/config/llm-profiles/default/current` | Get current default profile |\n\n### Provider Management\n\n| Action | Method | Endpoint | Description |\n|--------|--------|----------|-------------|\n| List Providers | GET | `/api/config/llm/providers` | Get available LLM providers |\n| Get Models | GET | `/api/config/llm/providers/{provider_name}/models` | Get models for a provider |\n\n## Provider Notes\n\n> **Tip:** Use `GET /api/config/llm/providers` to see all available providers and their supported models.\n>\n> **For OpenAI-compatible APIs:** If using a third-party provider that offers OpenAI-compatible endpoints (like local models, DeepSeek, or other proxies), use the `openai_compatible` provider and set the custom `base_url`.\n\n## Request Examples\n\n### Create Profile\n```json\nPOST /api/config/llm-profiles\n{\n  \"profile_name\": \"my-openai\",\n  \"provider\": \"openai\",\n  \"model\": \"gpt-4\",\n  \"api_key\": \"sk-...\",\n  \"temperature\": 0.7,\n  \"max_tokens\": 4096,\n  \"is_default\": false\n}\n```\n\n### Update Profile\n```json\nPUT /api/config/llm-profiles/my-openai\n{\n  \"temperature\": 0.5,\n  \"max_tokens\": 2048\n}\n```\n\n## Profile Fields\n\n| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n|-------|------|----------|-------------|\n| profile_name | string | Yes | Unique profile identifier |\n| provider | string | Yes | Provider name |\n| model | string | Yes | Model name |\n| api_key | string | Yes | API key for the provider |\n| base_url | string | No | Custom base URL |\n| temperature | float | No | Sampling temperature (0-2) |\n| max_tokens | int | No | Maximum tokens to generate |\n| top_p | float | No | Nucleus sampling |\n| frequency_penalty | float | No | Frequency penalty (-2 to 2) |\n| seed | int | No | Random seed |\n| description | string | No | Profile description |\n| is_default | bool | No | Set as default profile |\n\n## Workflow\n\n1. **Get available providers** → `GET /api/config/llm/providers`\n2. **Choose provider and model** → `GET /api/config/llm/providers/{provider}/models`\n3. **Create profile** → `POST /api/config/llm-profiles`\n4. **Set as default** (optional) → `POST /api/config/llm-profiles/{name}/set-default`\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775657137822}}
{"type":"message","id":"b789c3ae","parentId":"f603ccd7","timestamp":"2026-04-08T14:05:49.704Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the API. I need to create an LLM profile. But the user hasn't provided an API key. I need to ask them for an API key (OpenAI, Anthropic, DeepSeek, or compatible) to create the profile.\n\nWait - VibeSurf also supports openai_compatible providers. Maybe the user has a local LLM or a third-party API. But they haven't given me any credentials.\n\nI should ask the user for an LLM API key so I can create the profile.\n\nActually, wait - maybe VibeSurf has a built-in free tier or uses a specific provider that the user has already configured. But from the error, it clearly says \"No LLM profile available\". \n\nLet me ask the user for their API key or provider details so I can set up a profile. I could suggest using OpenAI or DeepSeek or ask what they want to use."},{"type":"text","text":"需要先创建一个 LLM profile 才能驱动浏览器。请提供你想使用的 LLM API：\n\n**方式一：OpenAI（推荐）**\n- 需要一个 `sk-...` 格式的 API Key\n\n**方式二：DeepSeek / 其他兼容 API**\n- 需要 `API Key` + `base_url`\n\n**方式三：本地模型**\n- 需要 `base_url`（如 `http://localhost:11434` 对应 Ollama）\n\n你有哪个可用的 LLM Key？或者想用哪个provider？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775657137864,"responseId":"062593b25e54be60fc6321b83846cf8b"}}
